            named <code>img</code>.
          </RoadmapCard>
          <RoadmapCard title="First-run wizard" status="shipped" eta="v1">
            Eight linear steps from password through hardware,
            capabilities, conditional HF token, license, install,
            done. Legacy 5-step picker and three IA prototypes deleted.
          </RoadmapCard>
        </RoadmapColumn>

        <RoadmapColumn title="Next" eyebrow="v0.2">
          <RoadmapCard title="Hugging Face model pulls" status="next">
